quran[112]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"ﾆ‖ttanike yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n hasboore maﾉ橡兎 nden fii golleeji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, kamﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 e nder welsindaare ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉rniiﾉ兎 gaayi Laakara on; sabu hilnagol(soklirde) maﾉ橡兎 aduna on [wedditoo fii Laakara on]."
  21,2,"Arataa e maﾉ橡兎 e Alqur'aana immorde ka Joomi maﾉ橡兎 jippiinde kesun, si wanaa ﾉ兎 heﾉ擁ke nde heﾉ預gol ngol aldaa e nafa, ko woni, ko heﾉ預gol fijindaaru hara ﾉ兎 haajaaka ko woni kon e nder mayre."
  21,3,"ﾆ‘ jenntii mo hari ﾉ兎rﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n ko welsindiiﾉ容 e makko, tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n suuﾉ擁ri keefeeru ngun yewtere nde ﾉ兎 gunndondirta nden e mu'un ko ﾉ兎 wi'uﾉ兎: "Enee,taw si oo nodditiiﾉ熔 wonnde ko o Nulaaﾉ熔 o wonaa si wanaa ﾉ殿nndunke yeru mon alaa ko o senndi on e makko?! ko o addi kon ko mbilewu, kaa on jokkay mo hara hiﾉ熔n anndi ko o ﾉ殿nndunke yeru mo'on, Te ko o addi kon kadi ko mbilewu?!"
  21,4,"Nulaaﾉ熔 on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) maaki: "Joomi am, hiMo Anndi ko suuﾉ蓉ﾉ熔n kon ka yewtere, ko Kanko woni Annduﾉ熔 kala konngol ngol wowloowo wowli ka kammuli e ka leydi, Kanko ko O Nanoowo konnguﾉ擁 jeyaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, Annduﾉ熔 golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, aray O Yoﾉ殿 ﾉ兎 e dow ﾉ蓉m."
  21,5,")Ko woni, ﾉ兎 skkki sikkin e fiyaake ko Muhammadu addi kon (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna), tuma goo ﾉ兎 wi'a: "Ko koyﾉ擁 jillondirﾉ擁 firo alanaa ﾉ擁".Tumo goo kadi ﾉ兎 wi'a: "Wanaa non, ko woni, o fefindi ﾉ擁, ﾉ擁 maraa lasili". Tuma goo kadi ﾉ兎 wi'a: "Kanko ko o yimoowo, awa si tawii o laatike goonguﾉ熔 e nodditagol makko ngol yo o addan men kaawa- seeji, yeru tuggordu Muusaa ndun, e Naaqawa Saalihu mban"."
  21,6,"Gomﾉ擁naano ado ﾉ兎e weeﾉ妬tuﾉ兎 feere, saare toriinde feere fii jippineede Aayeeje ﾉ容n ﾉ兎 okkaa nden feere wano ﾉ兎 toririinde non, ko woni ﾉ兎 fennu Aayeeje ﾉ容n si Men halki ﾉ兎. Mbela ﾉ兎eﾉ熔o kadi gomﾉ擁nay?"
  21,7,"Men Nulaali ado maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- si wanaa worﾉ兎 immorde e ﾉ殿nndunke Men wahayina e maﾉ橡兎, Men Nulaali ﾉ兎 Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎, lanndee tun yimﾉ兎 defte ﾉ兎n ado mo'on si tawii on anndaa ﾉ蓉m."
  21,8,"Men waﾉ預ali Nulaaﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 Men Nuli ﾉ兎n joomiraa- ﾉ兎 ﾉ殿lli ﾉ兎 ﾃｱaamataa ﾃｱaametee on, ko woni, hiﾉ兎 ﾃｱaama wano ﾃｱaamirta tanaa maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 wonaali heddotooﾉ兎 ka aduna hara ﾉ兎 maayataa."
  21,9,"Refti Men Goongani Nulaaﾉ兎 Amen ﾉ兎n ko Men fodi ﾉ兎 kon, nokku ka Men danndi ﾉ兎 halkeede wonndude e ﾉ兎 Men Muuyi ﾉ兎n immorde e gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, Min halki yawtuﾉ兎 keerol ﾉ兎n sabu yeddugol maﾉ橡兎 Alla, e waﾉ遼擁tagol maﾉ橡兎 geddi ﾉ擁n."
  21,10,"Goﾉ擁i Men jippinii e mooﾉ熔n Alqur'aanaare nden no e mayre teddungal mo'on ngal e wasu mo'on ngun si on gomﾉ擁nii nde, on gollirii ko woni kon e mayre. Kaa on alaa hakkilannde ﾉ蓉m, sakko yaccoﾉ熔n faade e gomﾉ擁nngol nde, e gollirngol ko woni kon e nder mayre?!"
  21,11,"Kaawee ko heewiri wa ca'e ﾉ容 Men halki ﾉ蓉m sabu tooﾃｱirgol majje keefeeru ngun, Men Tagi ﾉ殿awo majje yimﾉ兎 goo!"
  21,12,"Tuma nde halkanooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n yi'unoo Lepte mulayﾉ容 ﾉ容n, tawi kamﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 yaccoo doga saare maﾉ橡兎 nden immorde e [kulol] halkeede."
  21,13,"ﾆ‘ noddiroyee fii jalnorgol: "Wata on dogu dey, yiltee(nduttee) faade e ko wonunoﾉ熔n e mu'un kon immorde e neemaaji e dakammeeji mo'on, e koﾉ預nﾉ容 mo'on kadi; belajo'o on lannditoyte goﾉ遼蓉 e fii aduna mo'on on"."
  21,14,"ﾆ‘e tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 qirritoyoo bakkatuuji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n ﾉ兎 wi'a: "Eeyoo, halakuyee amen e hayrere amen, pellet, menen men woniino tooﾃｱuﾉ兎 sabu yeddugol amen Alla"."
  21,15,"Seerataa qirritagol maﾉ橡兎 bakkatuuji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n e noddugol maﾉ橡兎 e wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n halakuyee, noddaandu maﾉ橡兎 ndu ﾉ兎 fillitotoo ndun haa Men waﾉ預 ﾉ兎 yeru remuru soﾃｱaandu, ko ﾉ兎 maayuﾉ兎 dillugol alanaa ﾉ兎."
  21,16,"Men tagiraali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji fijindaaru e puyndan, ko woni, Men tagiriiﾉ擁 fii tinndinorﾉ擁 e Kattanﾉ容 Amen."
  21,17,"Sinndo Men faalano jogitaade sonnaajo maaﾉ蓉m ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 Men jogitotono ﾉ蓉m ko woni kon ka Amen, Men wonaali non waﾉ熔oﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉m sabu Senagol Amen e ﾉ蓉m."
  21,18,"Ko woni Meﾉ容n werloo Goonga ka Men wahayini kan faade e Nulaaﾉ兎 Amen ﾉ兎n e dow meere yimﾉ兎 geddi ﾉ兎n ka fuyna nde, tawa meere maﾉ橡兎 nden ko yahunde iwi fes, no woodani on -onon wi'uﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n hiMo jogitii sonnaajo e ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔- halkaare sabu ko sifiﾉ熔n Mo kon ko O hanndaa e mu'un."
  21,19,"Ko Kanko Tun woodani O Senike laamu kammuu- li ﾉ擁n e Laamu leydi ndin, ﾉ兎n womﾉ兎 ka Makko kadi immorde e Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 mawnikin- taaka Dewal Makko ngal, ﾉ兎 tampirtaa ngal."
  21,20,"Hiﾉ兎 duumii e Subhinanagol Alla e duumaade, ﾉ兎 haaﾉ殿taa e ﾉ蓉m."
  21,21,"Ko woni, sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n jogiti reweteeﾉ擁 gaanin Alla, ﾉ擁 wuurtintaa mayﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ko honno ﾉ兎 rewirta ronkuﾉ熔 gaayi ﾉ蓉m?!"
  21,22,"Si tawiino laatino ka kammuuli e ka leydi reweteeﾉ擁 ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 ﾉ擁ﾉ擁-kala ﾉ擁 bonirayno pooﾉ熔ndiral reweteeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka laamu, ko selli kon no lunndii ﾉ蓉m, Alla Jom Arsi kin O Senike gaayi ko sirkoﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n sifotoo Mo kon fenaande wonndema no woodani Mo kafidaaﾉ兎."
  21,23,"Alla ko Kanko woni teelﾉ熔 e Laamu Makko ngun e ﾃ疎awoore Makko nden, hay e gooto lanndotaako Mo fii ko O hoddir kon e ko O ﾃ疎awi kon, Kanko le O lanndoyto jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n gaayi golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, O yoﾉ殿 ﾉ兎 e dow ﾉ蓉m."
  21,24,"Ko woni, ﾉ兎 jogiti gaanin Alla reweteeﾉ擁, maakan an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎: "Addee hujja mon on e hanndugol rewugol ﾉ擁, awa ndee Deftere jippinaa- nde e am, e Defte jippinaaﾉ容 ﾉ容n e Nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n on maraa hujja e nder majje, ko woni, ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 tuugutaako si wanaa e majjere e ﾃｱemmbugol, hara kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉rniiﾉ兎 e jaﾉ砥gol Goonga kan."
  21,25,"Men Nulaali ado maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- Nulaaﾉ熔 woo si wanaa Men wahayinii e makko pellet, reweteeﾉ熔 alaa e Goonga si wanaa Miin Rewee Lam Min Tun, wata on kafidu(renndinee) e Am hay e huunde."
  21,26,"Sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'i: "Alla jogitike Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 rewﾉ兎." O Senike O Laaﾉ妬i e ﾉ容n penaali ﾉ容 ﾉ兎 wowlata Mo, ko ﾉ兎 Teddinaaﾉ兎 ka Makko, ko woni, Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ko Jeyaaﾉ兎 Alla, Teddinaaﾉ兎 ka Makko ﾆ‖ttinaaﾉ兎 e Makko."
  21,27,"ﾆ‘ adortaa Joomi maﾉ橡兎 konngol, ﾉ兎 wowlataa ﾉ蓉m haa O Yamira ﾉ兎, kamﾉ兎 ko Yamiroore Makko nden ﾉ兎 gollata, ﾉ兎 lunndantaako Mo Yamiroore."
  21,28,"HiMo Anndi ko yawti kon e ko aroyta kon e golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 torotaako tefoore nden si wanaa e sakkitoore mo O welnaa tefoore mu'un, kamﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 reenii immorde e kulol Makko O Senike, ﾉ兎 lunndotaako Mo e Yamiroore wanaa kadi haﾉ熔ore."
  21,29,"Kala wi'uﾉ熔 immorde e Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e noone hottagol: "Min ko mi reweteeﾉ熔 gaanin Alla". Menen Men Yoﾉ妬ray mo konngol makko ngol lepte Jahannama ﾃ疎lnde Darngal ko o luttinteeﾉ熔 e majje, ko yeru ndii njoﾉ電i Men yoﾉ殿ta tooﾃｱirﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n keefaraagal e sirkanngol Alla."
  21,30,"Kaa ﾉ兎n yeddu ﾉ兎 Alla anndaali woni; wonndema kammuuli ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin woniino notondirﾉ擁, hari heneere alaa hakkunde majji sakko toﾉ登 jippoo e mayre, Men senndi hakkunde majji, Men waﾉ擁 ka ndiyam iwuﾉ預am ka kammu saaﾆｴi ka leydi kala huunde immorde e muumi maaﾉ蓉n puﾉ擁. Kaa ﾉ兎e taskotaako ﾉ蓉m, ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁na Alla Kanko Tun?!"
  21,31,"Men Tagi ka leydi pelle tabituﾉ容 fii wata ndi dimbodu e ko woni kon hoore mayri, Men waﾉ擁 e mayri laawi yaajuﾉ擁 belajo'o kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 feeway ka jahe maﾉ橡兎 faade e faandaaje maﾉ橡兎."
  21,32,"Men waﾉ擁 kammu ngun kippude reenaandi immorde yanugol ko aldaa e tugaale, e reenaangu immorde e wujjugol nanﾉ容, sirkirooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ko woni kon ka kammu immorde e Aayeeje -wano naange ngen e lewru ndun- ko ﾉ蓉rniiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 taskotaako."
  21,33,"Alla Kanko Tun woni Taguﾉ熔 jemma on fii ka fowtee, O Tagi ﾃｱalal ngal ka ngurdan faggitee, O Tagi naange ngen maande fii ﾃｱalorma on, lewru ndun kadi maande fii jemma on, kala majji immorde e naange ngen e lewru ndun hiﾉ擁 doga e yiilornde majji heeraniinde ﾉ擁, ﾉ擁 selataa nde ﾉ擁 ooﾃｱataako."
  21,34,"Men waﾉ預naali hay e gooto e ﾉ殿nndunke ado maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- luttineewo e ﾉ預m ngurndam, e hara si lajal maa ngal timmii e ﾉ預'am ngurndam maayuﾉ預a, hara ko kamﾉ兎 woni heddotoo ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ殿awo maaﾉ預? ﾉ蓉n waﾉ預taa."
  21,35,"Kala wonkii, woni ko gomﾉ擁nki maa ko yedduki ki meeﾉ預y mayde nden ka aduna, Men jarriboo on -onon yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- ka ngurndan aduna e to'e e neema e tampere, refti ﾉ殿awo mayde mon nden ko ka Amen wanaa ka tanaa Amen rutteteﾉ熔n."
  21,36,"Si yi'ii ma -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 jogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde hiﾉ兎 raﾉ熔ra jokkuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'igol maﾉ橡兎: "Enee, ko oo woni yennude reweteeﾉ擁 mo'on ﾉ擁 wonﾉ熔n rewude ﾉ擁n?!" Hara ﾉ兎 jalnorte woni, ko ﾉ兎 yedduﾉ兎 ko Alla jippini kon e maﾉ橡兎 immorde ka Alqur'aanaare e ko O okki ﾉ兎 kon e neemaaji ko ﾉ兎 yeddu ﾉ兎; ko kamﾉ兎 hanndi e ayiibe on sabu hawtindirgol maﾉ橡兎 kala bone."
  21,37,"Neﾉ遼熔 on Tagaama e heﾃｱaare, kanko himo heﾃｱora piiji ﾉ擁n ado waﾉ蓉gol majji, ko sabu ﾉ蓉m si sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n no heﾃｱara Lepte ﾉ容n, aray Mi holla on -onon heﾃｱorﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Lepte Am ﾉ容n- ko heﾃｱornoﾉ熔n kon e ﾉ蓉m, wata on ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥 yaccinaneede ﾉ蓉m."
  21,38,"Heeferﾉ兎 yedduﾉ兎 Immital ﾉ兎n hiﾉ兎 wi'ude e noone heﾃｱorgol: "Ko honnde tuma ko foduﾉ熔n men kon laatotoo -ko onon yo Julﾉ兎- immorde e Immital si tawii ko on goonguﾉ兎 e kon ko nodditiﾉ熔n waﾉ蓉gol mum."
  21,39,"Sinndo ﾉ兎e heeferﾉ兎 yedduﾉ兎 Immital annduno tuma tawi ﾉ兎 ruttataa Yiite ngen gaayi geece maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n wanaa gaayi ﾉ殿bbe maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n kdai, wonnde kadi walloowo alaa mo no walla ﾉ兎 duﾃｱugol Lepte ﾉ容n gaayi maﾉ橡兎, sinndo ﾉ兎 yananano ﾉ蓉m ﾉ兎 heﾃｱortaano Lepte ﾉ容n."
  21,40,"Ngee Yiite nge ﾉ兎 leptetee e mu'un nge arataa e maﾉ橡兎 e anndal maﾉ橡兎, ko woni, nge aray e maﾉ橡兎 e juhayee, hara ﾉ兎 hattantaake yiltugol nge e maﾉ橡兎, wanaa kamﾉ兎 woni nennanoyteeﾉ兎 haa ﾉ兎 tuuba Hinnayee on hewta ﾉ兎."
  21,41,"Si tawii yimﾉ兎 maaﾉ預 ﾉ兎n jalkitii ma, haray wanaa an ﾉ蓉m fuﾉ遼熔ri, gomﾉ擁i jalkitanoo ma Nulaaﾉ兎 ado maaﾉ預 -an Nulaaﾉ熔- O huﾉ妬ndii yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎n laatinooﾉ兎 no jalkita ﾉ兎 Lepte ﾉ容n ﾉ兎n laatinooﾉ兎 no jalnora ﾉ兎 ka aduna tuma nde Nulaaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n hulﾉ妬nirta ﾉ兎."
  21,42,"Maakan -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾉ兎e heﾃｱorayﾉ兎 Lepte: "Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e ﾃｱalorma e kon ko Hinnorante On muuyani on immorde e jippinngol Lepte ﾉ容n e halkugol on?" ko woni, kamﾉ兎 gaayi jaﾅ逆aade waajuuji Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n e hujjaaji Makko ﾉ擁n ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉rniiﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 taskotaako hay e huunde e ﾉ蓉m sabu majjere e njofoyaagal."
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani ﾉ兎 reweteeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 no dannda ﾉ兎 Lepte Amen ﾉ容n? ﾆ‘ hattantaake wallirde wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n martinngol lorra e majji, ﾉ兎 anndantaa ﾉ擁 nafa, mo wallaali wonkii mun ko honno o wallirta tanaa makko?! wanaa kamﾉ兎 kadi woni walloyteeﾉ兎 immorde e Lepte Amen ﾉ容n."
  21,44,"Ko woni Men dakmitii ﾉ兎e yedduﾉ兎, Men dakmitiri baabiraaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n sabu ko Men weeﾉ妬tani ﾉ兎 immorde e neemaaji Amen; ka ﾉ預ynugol ﾉ兎, haa jamaanu ngun juutani ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 hoditori ﾉ蓉m, ﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiﾉ妬 e geddi maﾉ橡兎. Kaa hara ﾉ兎e hoditorﾉ兎 neemaaji Amen heﾃｱorﾉ兎 Lepte Amen yi'aali wonnde Menen Meﾉ容n ara e leydi ndin Men uytira ndi e bannﾅ菊eji mayri doolnugol Amen yimﾉ兎 mayri, e Polgal Amen e hoore maﾉ橡兎, sakko ﾉ兎 taskoo ﾉ蓉m fii wata yanu e maﾉ橡兎 ko yani kon e tanaa maﾉ橡兎?! ﾆ‘e laataaki fooluﾉ兎, ko woni, kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 foolaaﾉ兎."
  21,45,"Maaku -an Nulaaﾉ熔-: "Anndu ko mi hulﾉ妬nirta on -onon yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- immorde eLepte Alla ko Wahayu mo Joomi am Wahyini e Am on, faaﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 on nana- taa Goonga ka ﾉ兎 noddaa kan e mu'un nanﾉ容 jaﾉ砥gol si ﾉ兎 hulﾉ妬niraama Lepte Alla ﾉ容n."
  21,46,"Mi woondii si meemii ﾉ兎e ﾉ預ﾉ橡殿yﾉ兎 yaccinaneede Lepte ﾉ容n geﾉ殿l immorde e Lepte Joomi maaﾉ預 ﾉ容n -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ma ﾉ兎 wi'u ontuma: "Eeyoo, halakuyee amen e hayrere amen, menen men laatike tooﾃｱirﾉ兎 sirkanngol Alla e fennugol ko Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) Addi kon "."
  21,47,"Men darna Manndikirﾉ容 nunﾉ蓉ﾉ容 ﾉ容n fii yimﾉ兎 Darngal ngal fii yo ﾉ容 manndikire golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, tooﾃｱirtaake e nder nden ﾃ疎laande hay wonkii uytaneede moﾆｴﾆｴi makko ﾉ擁n maaﾉ蓉m ﾉ兎ydaneede bonﾉ容 makki, hay si laatike ko peesirgal ngal no famﾉ擁ri wa yeru ko abbere khardal manndike ﾉ蓉m Men adday ﾉ蓉m, Men yonii hasbooﾉ兎 Meﾉ容n hasba golle jeyaaﾉ兎 Amen ﾉ兎n."
  21,48,"Gomﾉ擁i Men Okkii Muusaa e Haaruuna (yo ﾉ兎 his) Tawreetaare senndaynde hakkunde Goonga kan e meere nden e hakkunde ko dagii e ko harmi, ko nde Peewal wonannde ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 nde, ko nde waaju wonannde hulooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Joomi mu'un."
  21,49,"ﾆ‘n hulayﾉ兎 Lepte Joomi maﾉ橡兎 On mo ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁ni ﾉ蓉m fii kala ﾉ兎 yi'aali mo, hara kamﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 huli Darngal ngal."
  21,50,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare Jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) ko nde waaju wonannde on faalaaﾉ熔 waajitornde nde heewunde nafa e moﾆｴﾆｴere. Kaa hara onon on yedday nde wonndude ﾉ蓉m? Hara on qirritaaki ko woni kon e mayre on gollirtaa nde?"
  21,51,"Gomﾉ擁i Men Okkii Ibraahiima Hujja e dow yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n ila ka cukaaku makko hari Men woniino kadi Annduﾉ兎 mo, Men Okki mo ko o hanndi kon e mu'un e Ganndal Amen immorde e Hujja e dow yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n."
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko Aajara e yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n: "Ko honﾉ蓉m woni ﾉ擁i sanamuuji ﾉ擁 moﾆｴﾆｴinirﾉ熔n juuﾉ容 mon ﾉ容n, ﾃｱiiﾉ砥ﾉ熔n e rewgol ﾉ擁?""
  21,53,"Yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n wi'ani mo: "Men tawii baabiraaﾉ兎 amen ﾉ兎n no rewaﾉ擁, men rewiriﾉ擁 ﾃｱemmbugol ﾉ兎"."
  21,54,"Ibraahiima Maakani ﾉ兎: "Gomﾉ擁i on wonii -onon jokkuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- e baabiraaﾉ兎 mo'on sincuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e nder majjere ﾉ殿nngunde gaayi Laawol Goongo ngol."
  21,55,"Yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n wi'ani mo: "Enee, ko soobee addaﾉ預a men, fewndo wowluﾉ預a ko wowluﾉ預a kon, kaa an ko e fijooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n jeyaﾉ預a?""
  21,56,"Ibraahiima maaki: "Ko woni, ko soobee mi addani on wanaa samakala, Joomi mooﾉ熔n ko Kanko woni Jooma kammuuli ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin On Taguﾉ熔 ﾉ擁 ko aldaa e misal adiingal, min wonndema pellet, Joomi mo'on e Jooma kammuuli ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin miﾉ熔 jeyaa e seediiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, laatanaaki sanamuuji mo'on ﾉ擁n geﾉ殿l immorde e ﾉ蓉m."
  21,57,"Ibraahiima maaki nokku ka yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n nanataa: "Mi woondii, bee tun mi fewja fii ﾉ擁i sanamuuji mo'on ko mettatata on ﾉ殿awo yahugol mon ka juldeere mo'on accaﾉ擁."
  21,58,"Ibraahiima munci sanamuuji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n haa ﾉ擁 wonti kuntoy tosokoy, o acci mawndu majji jorto nde ﾉ兎 yiltitotoo e mayru fii yo ﾉ兎 lanndo ndu ko hommbo munci ﾉ擁."
  21,59,"Tuma nde ﾉ兎 ruttinoo ﾉ兎 tawi sanamuuji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n muncaama, yoga e maﾉ橡兎 lanndii yoga: "Ko hommbo munci reweteeﾉ擁 me'en ﾉ擁n? Pellet, on muncuﾉ熔 ﾉ擁 ko e tooﾃｱooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n o jeyaa, nokku ka o hoyni ﾉ熔n ko haani mawninnde e laﾉ橡妬nnde kon"."
  21,60,"Yoga maﾉ橡兎 wi'i: "Men naniino suka no wowlaﾉ擁 ko boni himo aybina ﾉ擁 himo wi'ee Ibraahiima, no gasa hara ko kanko munci ﾉ擁"."
  21,61,"Koohooﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n wi'i: "Addee Ibraahiima yeeso yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 yi'a mo; belajo'o ﾉ兎 seedoto himo qirritoo ko o huuwi kon, qirritagol makko ngol laatanoo on hujja e hoore makko"."
  21,62,"ﾆ‘ addi Ibraahiima (yo o his) ﾉ兎 lanndii mo: "Enee, Ibraahiima ko an golle ﾉ容e golle kaanuﾉ容 e sanamuuji amen ﾉ擁n?"!"
  21,63,"Ibraahiima maaki -ko o jalnoroowo ﾉ兎, ko o fenﾃｱinﾉ熔 ronkugol sanamuuji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n yeeso yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n-: "Mi waﾉ預ali ﾉ蓉m, ko woni, gollii ﾉ蓉m mawndu sanamuuji ﾉ擁n, lanndee sanamuuji mo'on ﾉ擁n si ﾉ擁 laatike hiﾉ擁 wowla"."
  21,64,"ﾆ‘ ruttori e wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n miijitagol e teskagol ﾉ殿nngani ﾉ兎 wonnde sanamuuji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n, ﾉ擁 nafataa ﾉ擁 lorrataa, ko kamﾉ兎 woni tooﾃｱuﾉ兎 fewndo ﾉ兎 rewunooﾉ擁 gaanin Alla."
  21,65,"Refti ﾉ兎 ruttii e sanndalﾉ預aku e geddi, ﾉ兎 wi'i: "Gomﾉ擁i hiﾉ預 yananaa -an Ibraahiima- pellet, ﾉ擁i sanamuuji ﾉ擁 wowlataa, ko honno yamirirtaa men yo men lanndo ﾉ擁?" ﾆ‘ faandori ﾉ蓉m hujja maﾉ橡兎 on, ﾉ蓉m wonti hujja e hoore maﾉ橡兎."
  21,66,"Ibraahiima maaki -ka mettinanngol ﾉ兎-: "Enee, on reway gaanin Alla sanamuuji ﾉ擁 nafataa on hay e huunde ﾉ擁 lorrataa on hay e huunde, kannji ko ﾉ擁 ronkuﾉ擁 e riiwgol lorra kan gaayi ko'e majji, maaﾉ蓉m pooﾉ蓉gol nafa kan fii majji."
  21,67,"On kaanii, ko rewoton kon kadi ko woori Alla kaanii, ﾉ擁i sanamuuji ﾉ擁 nafataa ﾉ擁 lorrataa kadi, enee, on hakkiltaa ﾉ蓉m, ﾉ預lon rewugol ﾉ擁?!"
  21,68,"Tuma nde ﾉ兎 ronkunoo tiindorde mo dalil ﾉ兎 wallitori doole ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 wi'i: "Sunniree Ibraahiima yiite ngen; wallee sanamuuji mo'on ﾉ擁 o fusi o munci ﾉ擁n si tawii on wonii waﾉ預yﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉m lepte haﾉ熔oje"."
  21,69,"ﾆ‘ huﾉ橡妬ni yiite ﾉ兎 werlii mo e magge, Men Daali: "ko an yo yiite, wonu ﾉ砥uﾉ登l e kisiyee e dow Ibraahiima, nge woniri non, o heﾉ殿ali lorra"."
  21,70,"Yimﾉ兎 Ibraahiima (yo o his) ﾉ兎n faandanii mo pewje fii sunnugol mo, Men bonni pewje maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, Men waﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 kamﾉ兎 halkaaﾉ兎 foolaa."
  21,71,"Men ndanndi mo Men ndanndi kadi Luutu, Men yaltini ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 yahi ka leydi Saami ndin ndi Men barkiniri e mu'un; Nulugol Annabaaﾉ兎 e mayri, e sabu ko Men saakani kon tageefooji ﾉ擁n e nder mayri immorde e moﾆｴﾆｴereeji."
  21,72,"Men Okki mo Ishaaqa fewndo o torinoo Joomi makko yo O arsiku mo ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔, Men Okki mo Yaaquuba ka ﾉ兎ydugol, gooto-kala immorde e Ibraahiima e geﾉ預ljo makko on Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba Men waﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ熔ftiiﾉ兎 Alla."
  21,73,"Men waﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 Almaamiiﾉ兎, yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n no feewira sabu maﾉ橡兎 e moﾆｴﾆｴere nden, hiﾉ兎 nodda yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n faade e dewal Alla Kanko tun e duﾅ蟻yee Makko O Toowii, Men wahayini e maﾉ橡兎 gollee moﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ擁n, tottiron Julde nden e noone ﾉ砥rﾉ熔 timmude, Itton Jakka on, wonon ﾉ熔ftiiﾉ兎 Men."
  21,74,"E Luutu Men Okki mo serndugol ﾃｱaawoore nden hakkunde wennjiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, Men Okki mo kadi Ganndal e fiyaake Diina makko, Men Hisini mo kadi immorde e lepte ﾉ擁 Men jippini ﾉ容n e dow saare makko nden (Saduuma) nde yimﾉ兎 mu'un laatinoo no huuwa boneeji ﾉ擁n, pellet, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 laatinoke yimﾉ兎 bonﾉ兎 yaltuﾉ兎 e ﾉ熔ftaare Joomi maﾉ橡兎."
  21,75,"Men naadi mo e nder Yurmeende Amen tuma nde Men danndunoo mo immorde e ﾉ容n lepte heﾉ砥nooﾉ容 yimﾉ兎 makko, pellet, kanko ko o jeyaaﾉ熔 e moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎n yamitorayﾉ兎 Yamiroore Amen, ﾉ兎 haﾉ擁tora kadi haﾉ熔ore Amen nden."
  21,76,"Jaﾅ逆o kadi -an Nulaaﾉ熔- fillayee fii Nuuhu; tuma nde o noddunoo Alla ko adii Ibraahiima e Luutu, Men jaabinirani mo okkugol mo ko o ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬 kon, Men ndanndi yimﾉ兎 makko gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n immorde e suno mawngo ngon."
  21,77,"Men ndanndi mo e hoﾉ熔 ﾉ兎n yimﾉ兎 fennuﾉ兎 ko Men Semmbiniri mo kon immorde e Aayeeje tinndinﾉ容 ﾉ容n e goongugol makko. Pellet, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 laatinoke yimﾉ兎 bone e lorra, Men halkiri ﾉ兎 fow maﾉ橡兎 yooleede."
  21,78,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- fillayee fii Daawuuda e geﾉ預ljo makko on Sulaymaana (yo ﾉ兎 his) tuma nde ﾃｱaawaynoo e muraadu addaandu ka maﾉ橡兎 e fiyaake wennjiiﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔; no woodani goﾉ遼熔 e maﾉ橡兎 dammi ﾉ擁 saakii jemma e nder ngesa oya mban ﾉ擁 bonni mba, Men woni Seediiﾉ兎 ﾃｱaawoore Daawuuda e Sulaymaana nden, wirnaaki e Amen immorde e ﾃｱaawoore maﾉ橡兎 nden hay e huunde."
  21,79,"Men Faamini Sulaymaana ﾃｱaawoore nden gaanin baaba makko Daawuuda, ﾉ兎 fow, immorde e Daawuuda e Sulaymaana Men Okki mo Annabaaku ngun e Ganndal fii ﾃｱaawoje Sari'a ﾉ容n, Men hertinanaali ﾉ蓉m Sulaymaana kanko tun, Men elti wonndude e Daawuuda pelle ﾉ容n hiﾉ容 subuhinora subuhinaali makko ﾉ擁n, Men eltani mo kadi colli ﾉ擁n, Men woni huuwooﾉ兎 ngol faaminngol e okkugol ﾃｱeeﾃｱal e ganndal e eltugol."
  21,80,"Men Anndini Daawuuda gaanin Sulaymaana tafogol mekeﾃｱaaji (dollokaaji njanndi) fii yo ﾉ擁 hiwu on e hewtugol jogaaji ﾉ擁n ka ﾉ殿lli mo'on. Enee, onon -ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎- on jarnay oo neema mo Alla neeminiri on ﾉ蓉m."
  21,81,"Men eltani Sulaymaana henndu ndun ko ndu saﾉ葉undu wifugol hindu doga e yamiroore makko tuma nde o yamiri ndu faade ka leydi Saami ndi Men barkiniri e mu'un sabu ko Men Nuli kon e mayri immorde e Annabaaﾉ兎, e moﾆｴﾆｴi weftaaﾉ擁 e mayri, Men laatike kala huunde ko Men annduﾉ兎, hay e huunde suuﾉ熔taako Men e ﾉ蓉m."
  21,82,"Men elti immorde e Seytanuuji ﾉ擁n, ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁 no mutana mo ka maaje ﾉ擁 yaltina lu'ulu'uuje e tanaa mu'un, hiﾉ擁 golla kadi ko wonaa ﾉ蓉m immorde e golle wano mahugol, Men laatike ko Men Reenuﾉ兎 limoore majji e golle majji, hay e huunde e ﾉ蓉m fuutataako Men."
  21,83,"Jaﾅ逆ii -an Nulaaﾉ熔- fillayee fii Ayyuuba (yo o his), tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko O Senike tuma nde jarrabuyee on heﾉ砥noo mo ko o wi'uﾉ熔: "Ko an yo Jooma, min dey mi hennaama ﾃｱaw e waaseede ﾉ兎ynguure nden, ko An woni ﾆ「rﾉ熔 Yurmeende yurmeteeﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fow, martin e am ﾉ蓉m ko heﾉ妬 lam"."
  21,84,"Men jaabi toraare makko nden, Men ittini mo ko heﾉ妬 mo kon immorde e lorra, Men okkiti mo ko o hattinoo kon immorde e ﾉ兎ynguure makko e geﾉ預l ﾉ兎 makko, Men okkiti mo wano maﾉ橡兎 wonndude e maﾉ橡兎, kala ﾉ蓉m Men waﾉ擁rii ﾉ蓉m Yurmeende immorde ka Amen, e waaju wonannde kala ﾉ熔ftorﾉ熔 Alla dewal; fii yo o munﾃｱor wano Ayyuuba munﾃｱornoo non."
  21,85,"Jaﾅ逆ii -an Nulaaﾉ熔- Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli (yo ﾉ兎 his), gooto-kala e maﾉ橡兎 ko e munﾃｱiiﾉ兎 jarrabuyee ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 jeyaa, e hoore daranagol kon ko Alla fawi ﾉ兎."
  21,86,"Men naadi ﾉ兎 e nder Yurmeende Amen, Men waﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 Annabaaﾉ兎, Men naadi ﾉ兎 ka Aljanna, pellet, kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 jeyaaﾉ兎 e jeyaaﾉ兎 Alla moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 gollirﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔ftaare Joomi maﾉ橡兎 nden, tawi gunndooji maﾉ橡兎 e kene maﾉ橡兎 no moﾆｴﾆｴi."
  21,87,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- fillayee fii jom linngii ngil Yuunusa (yo o his), tum nde o yahunoo ko aldaa e duﾅ蟻yee(sakkitgol immorde ka Joomi makko ko o tikkanﾉ熔 yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n sabu duumagol maﾉ橡兎 e geddi ﾉ擁n, o sikki wonnde Menen Men ﾉ妬ttinan-taa mo; leptirgol fii ko o yahi kon, o jarriboraa saﾉ葉ude ﾉ妬tteede e dummbeede fewndo linngil ngil moﾉ蓉noo mo, o noddi ka nder niﾉ兎 reedu linngil ngil e maayo ngon e jemma on; ko o qirritiiﾉ熔 bakkaatu makko on tuubuﾉ熔 ka Alla immorde e ﾉ蓉m, o wi'i: "Reweteeﾉ熔 e goonga alaa tanaa Maaﾉ預, A Senike A Laaﾉ妬i, min dey mi wonii jeyaaﾉ熔 e tooﾃｱuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n"."
  21,88,"Men jaabinani mo, Men danndiri mo immorde e saﾉ葉eende suno ngon yaltinngol mo ka nder niﾉ兎, e ka nder reedu linngil ngil, ko yeru no Yuunusa danndiranoo nii e ndee saﾉ葉eende makko ﾉ熔o Men danndirta gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n si ﾉ兎 yanii e saﾉ葉eende ﾉ兎 torike Alla."
  21,89,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- fillayee Jakariyaa (yo o his) tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko Senayee wonanii Mo o maaki: "Jooma, wata A accan ko mi teelﾉ熔 hara mi alaa ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔, ko An woni ﾆ「rﾉ熔 Moﾆｴﾆｴude heddotooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, arsikam ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 mo no heddoo ﾉ殿awo am"."
  21,90,"Men jaabinani mo toraare makko nden, Men Okki mo Yahyaa ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔, Men moﾆｴﾆｴini sonnaajo makko on, o wonti jibinoowo ﾉ殿awo hari o laatinoke dimaro, pellet, Jakariyaa e sonna makko e geﾉ預ljo makko on ﾉ兎 laatinoke hiﾉ兎 heﾃｱoo faade e gollugol moﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ擁n, ﾉ兎 laatinoke hiﾉ兎 nodda Men hara ko ﾉ兎 rerﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ko woni kon ka Amen immorde mbarjaari ndin, hara ko ﾉ兎 huluﾉ兎 kon ko woni ka Amen immorde e lepte ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 woniino yankinaniiﾉ兎 Men."
  21,91,"Jaﾅ逆o -an Nulaaﾉ熔- fillayee fii Mariyama (yo o his) on reenunooﾉ熔 farju makko on immorde e jeeno, Alla Nuli e makko Jibriila (yo o his), o wutti e makko o sowii Iisaa (yo o his), [Mariyama] e geﾉ預ljo makko on Iisaa ﾉ兎 laatike Maande e dow Bawﾉ容 Alla wonannde yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, wonndema pellet, hay e huunde ronkintaa Mo nokku ka O Tagi mo ko aldaa e baaba."
  21,92,"Pellet, kaa Diina mo'on -onon yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- ko Diina woota, ﾉ蓉m le ko Ngootimpaaku ngun ko ngun woni Diina Lismaamu kan, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on, Laﾉ橡妬nanee Lam dewal ngal Min tun."
  21,93,"Yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n seedi, tawi no e maﾉ橡兎 wootinﾉ擁nﾉ熔 e sirkuﾉ熔 e geddo e gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔, ﾉ兎e seeduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 fow maﾉ橡兎 ko ka Amen Menen tun ﾉ兎 artiroytee ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, Men yoﾉ殿 ﾉ兎 e dow golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n."
  21,94,"Kala e maﾉ橡兎 golluﾉ熔 golle moﾆｴﾆｴe ﾉ容n hara himo gomﾉ擁ni Alla e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on e ﾃ疎laande Sakkitiinde nden yiddugol alaa fii golle makko moﾆｴﾆｴe ﾉ容n, ko woni, Alla jarnay mo O sowana mo mbarjaari ndin, o tawoya ﾉ蓉m ka nder defter golle makko ﾃｱalnde o immintintee, o weltora ﾉ蓉m."
  21,95,"Gasantaa yimﾉ兎 saare nde Men halkiri ﾉ蓉m sabu geddi mayre nde ﾉ兎 ruttotoo ka aduna; fii yo ﾉ兎 tuubu tuubuubuyee maﾉ橡兎 on jaﾉ兎e."
  21,96,"ﾆ‘ ruttotaako poomaa haa si udditoyaama heedo Yaajuuja e Maajuuja ngon, hara kamﾉ兎 nden ﾃｱalnde e immorde kala ka towti e leydi nden hiﾉ兎 yalta hara ko ﾉ兎 heﾃｱiiﾉ兎."
  21,97,"Darngal ngal ﾉ殿dorii sabu yaltugol maﾉ橡兎, kulol maggal e caﾉ容ele maggal ﾉ容n feeﾃｱi, e jaka yoo gite yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n no udditii sabu saﾉ葉ude kulol maggal, ﾉ兎 wi'i: "Ee halkeede amen, gomﾉ擁i men laatinoke ka aduna e fijindaaru e welsindaare gaayi heblanagol ndee ﾃ疎laande Mawnde, ko woni men laatinoke tooﾃｱirﾉ兎 keefeeru e waﾉ遼擁tagol geddi ﾉ擁n."
  21,98,"Pellet, onon -ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎- e kon ko rewoton ko woori Alla immorde e sanamuuji ﾉ擁n, e ﾉ兎n weltorayﾉ兎 ko rewoton ﾉ兎 kon jeyaaﾉ兎 ka yimﾉ兎 e ka jinnaaji on wonoyay kuﾉ橡殿teeri Jahannama, onon e reweteeﾉ兎 mo'on ﾉ兎n on naatoyay e magge."
  21,99,"Sinndo ﾉ兎e rewaaﾉ兎 laatino reweteeﾉ兎 e Goonga ﾉ兎 naatataano ka Yiite wonndude e ﾉ兎n rewunoo- ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎, rewuﾉ兎 woo rewaaﾉ兎 woo ﾉ兎 fow maﾉ橡兎 hiﾉ兎 ka nder Yiite, ko ﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiﾉ登oﾉ兎 ton poomaa ﾉ兎 yaltataa e nder magge."
  21,100,"No woodani ﾉ兎 nder ton -sabu saﾉ葉ude muuseendiiji ko ﾉ兎 hawrondirta kon- foofaango sﾉ葉ungo, kamﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 ka Yiite ﾉ兎 nanataa hitooji ﾉ擁n immorde e saﾉ葉ude kulol ﾉ容nﾆｴinayngol ngol heﾉ砥ngol ﾉ兎."
  21,101,"Tuma nde sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wi'unoo: (Pellet, Iisaa e Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 rewanooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 naatoyay yiite ngen) Alla Daali: "Pellet, ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 Ganndal Alla aditii e fii mu'un wonnde ko ﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 Malal ngal wano Iisaa (yo o his) ko ﾉ兎 woﾉ遼擁nteeﾉ兎 gaayi Yiite ngen."
  21,102,"Yottotaako e nanﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n hito Jahannama, kamﾉ兎 hiﾉ兎 e nder ko wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n wooﾉ預a kon immorde e neemaaji e dakammeeji ﾉ擁n ko ﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiﾉ砥ﾉ兎, neemaaji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n taﾆｴataa poomaa."
  21,103,"Kulol mawngol ngol hulﾉ妬noytaaﾉ兎 tuma Yiite ngen rewnetee e dow yimﾉ兎 magge ﾉ兎n, Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n jaﾉ橡登ra ﾉ兎 jarnugol hara hiﾉ兎 wi'a: "Ko ndee woni ﾃ疎laande mo'on nde wonanoﾉ熔n fodeende nden ka aduna, hiﾉ熔n weltiniree nder ton ﾉ擁n neemaaji ﾉ擁 hawroton e mu'un"."
  21,104,"ﾃ疎lnde Men sowoyta kammu ngun yeru sowidugol ﾉ容rol e ko ngol wonndi kon e mu'un, Men mooﾉ登ya tageefo ngon e mbaadi maﾉ橡兎 ndi ﾉ兎 taganoo ndin e mu'un ka laawol aranol, Men fodii ﾉ蓉m fodoore nde lunndagol alaa e mu'un, pellet, Men laatike Siinooﾉ兎 ko Men fodi kon."
  21,105,"Gomﾉ擁i Men winndiino ka defte ﾉ容 Men Tillini ﾉ蓉m e dow Nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ殿awo hari Men winndii ﾉ蓉m ka Allauwal Reenaangal: "Pellet, leydi ndin ronoyay ndi jeyaaﾉ兎 Alla moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 gollirooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔ftaare Makko nden, ﾉ兎n le ko Mofte Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) ﾉ容n"."
  21,106,"Pellet, no e nder koo ko Men jippini immorde e waaju ngun ﾉ殿nngal wonannde yimﾉ兎 rewirooﾉ兎 Joomi mu'un ko O Sar'inani ﾉ兎 kon, ko kamﾉ兎 woni nafitorooﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉m."
  21,107,"Men Nuliraali ma -an Muhammadu- Nulaaﾉ熔 si wanaa Yurmeende denndaangal Tageefo ngon; sabu ko siforﾉ預a kon immorde e rerﾉ蓉gol fii fewnugol yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e danndugol ﾉ兎 immorde e Lepte Alla ﾉ容n."
  21,108,"Maaku -an Nulaaﾉ熔-: "Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am immorde e Joomi am ko wonndema Reweteeﾉ熔 mon On e Goonga ko Reweteeﾉ熔 Gooto, kafidaaﾉ熔 alanaa Mo ko Kanko woni Alla, ﾉ熔woree gomﾉ擁nngol Mo, e gollirgol ﾉ熔ftaare Makko nden"."
  21,109,"Si ﾉ兎e ﾉ蓉rnike ko adduﾉ預a kon, maakan ﾉ兎 -an Nulaaﾉ熔-: "Mi anndinii on wonndema min e mo'on fiyaake on no fota ﾉ殿nngude hakkunde am e mo'on, mi wonaali annduﾉ熔 ko honnde tuma jippintee e mooﾉ熔n ko Alla fodi kon immorde e Lepte Makko ﾉ容n."
  21,110,"Pellet, Alla no Anndi ko finﾃｱinto immorde e konngol ngol, hiMo Anndi kadi ko suuﾉ熔 ton kon e maggol, hay e huunde suuﾉ預naaki Mo e ﾉ蓉m, aray O Yoﾉ殿 on e dow ﾉ蓉m."
  21,111,"Mi anndaa, no gasa hara nennanngol on Lepte ﾉ容n ko ndarndagol on, e ﾉ預ynugol, e dakmitugol on haa dummunne happaaﾉ熔 e Ganndal Alla; fii yo on duumi e geddi mo'on e majjere mooﾉ熔n."
  21,112,"Nulaaﾉ熔 Alla on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) maaki ko O noddayﾉ熔 Jooma: "Jooma, senndir hakkunde amen e yimﾉ兎 amen ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎n deppitiiﾉ兎 e geddi ﾉ擁n ﾃ疎awoore Goongaare nden, ko Joomi amen Hinnorante On men wallitorta e dow ko wowloton immorde e geddi e fennugol ngol"."
